description: My place is on the Upper West Side, not far from the Museum of Natural History. You’ll love its perfect location, solitude, and proximity to the subway. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers.
name: Cozy 1BR & private bath near Central Park & more
review: Awesome location! A block away from a subway station and next to great bars/restaurants. Zak was great at communicating with us. Had a great time.
